2 (c) Moneys in the special fund shall be expended by the
3 office of the state fire marshal, with the support of the
4 department of law enforcement pursuant to part II of this
5 chapter, for the following purposes:
6 (1) Fire and life safety code administration,
7 implementation, and enforcement support;
8 (2) Fire prevention, wildfire mitigation, and community
9 risk reduction programs;
